OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FA Palestine Action activist who faced
OL,8,Ftrial accused of criminal damage over
OL,9,Fa raid at an Israel-linked defence
OL,10,Ffirm's UK site has said she will
OL,11,F"never regret" being involved in the
OL,12,Fdirect action.
OL,14,FZoe Rogers, 22, was cleared of
OL,15,Fcriminal damage over the break in at
OL,16,Fthe Elbit Systems factory in Bristol.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
