OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FShe was one of six activists who
OL,8,Fentered the site in the early hours of
OL,9,FAugust 6 2024 wearing red jumpsuits.
OL,10,FShe was accused of smashing drones
OL,11,Fwith a sledgehammer.
OL,13,FProsecutors said she and her co-
OL,14,Faccused had attempted to "cause as
OL,15,Fmuch damage as possible and obtain
OL,16,Finformation about the company" while
OL,17,Fthe group said they aimed to damage
OL,18,Fdrones and equipment to protect
OL,19,FPalestinians.
OL,26,@vD@ZOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
