CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FAsked why she took part in the break
OL,8,Fin, Ms Rogers told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "I signed petitions,
OL,10,Fspoke to my MP, went on marches, I
OL,11,Feven did a picket outside an arms
OL,12,Ffactory.
OL,14,F"And it was clear to me that none of
OL,15,Fit was working; the democratic process
OL,16,Fhad failed to protect Palestinians
OL,17,Ffrom genocide and the only option left
OL,18,Fwas to take direct action."
OL,26,@qD@NOUvD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
