OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FMs Rogers was tried alongside
OL,8,FCharlotte Head, Samuel Corner, Leona
OL,9,FKamio, Fatema Rajwani and Jordan
OL,10,FDevlin.
OL,12,FHead, Corner, Kamio and Rajwani were
OL,13,Fconvicted at Woolwich Crown Court last
OL,14,Fweek of criminal damage, while Corner
OL,15,Fwas found guilty of causing grievous
OL,16,Fbodily harm when he fractured a police
OL,17,Fofficer's spine during the raid.
OL,19,FMr Devlin and Ms Rogers were both
OL,20,Fcleared of criminal damage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
