SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FMs Rogers, who lives in east London,
OL,8,Fsaid the action, when the site was
OL,9,Fsmashed into with an old prison van
OL,10,Fand the six carried sledgehammers, was
OL,11,F"terrifying".
OL,13,F"It was terrifying because of the
OL,14,Flevel of violence we faced from both
OL,15,Fsecurity guards and police," she said.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@LO]uD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
