OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FProsecutors told their trial that as
OL,8,Fsecurity guards tried to stop the
OL,9,Fraid, they were sworn at and told to
OL,10,Fleave, had sledgehammers swung at them
OL,11,Fand were whipped, while one was
OL,12,Fsprayed with a foam fire extinguisher.
OL,14,FSecurity guard Angelo Volante told a
OL,15,Fprevious trial that the activists were
OL,16,F"armed and threatening us with harm"
OL,17,Fand in footage could be heard saying,
OL,18,F"if you swing that once more it's
OL,19,Fgoing to get really serious".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@dO]zD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
