SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FMr Volante, who took a sledgehammer
OL,8,Ffrom one of the defendants, denied
OL,9,Fswinging it at them, telling jurors:
OL,10,F"Being really serious did not mean
OL,11,Fusing the sledgehammer."
OL,13,FBut the defendants insisted violence
OL,14,Fwas not part of the plan, while Corner
OL,15,Fmaintained that he hit Police Sergeant
OL,16,FKate Evans to protect Kamio.
OL,18,FMs Rogers spent nearly 18 months in
OL,19,Fcustody while awaiting trial.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
