OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FAsked if she regrets her action, Ms
OL,8,FRogers said: "I'll never regret what I
OL,9,Fdid, because there is a good chance
OL,10,Fthat my actions, or all of our
OL,11,Factions, that night saved people's
OL,12,Flives.
OL,14,F"Obviously, I was not expecting to be
OL,15,Farrested for terrorism and held for
OL,16,Fthree times the length of the legal
OL,17,Flimit but no, I won't, I'll never
OL,18,Fregret my actions."
OL,26,@pD@NOUvD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
