OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FMs Rogers, who was 20 at the time of
OL,8,Fthe incident, said she admitted that
OL,9,Fshe damaged property but said "there
OL,10,Fare supposed to be protections in law
OL,11,Ffor people who damage property to save
OL,12,Flives".
OL,14,FOf her and Mr Devlin being cleared,
OL,15,Fshe said: "Anything I say on it will
OL,16,Fbe speculation, but I think it is
OL,17,Fclear that the jury didn't want to
OL,18,Fconvict us of criminal damage despite
OL,19,Fthe fact that we both said we damaged
OL,20,Fproperty.
OL,26,@qD@_OUtD@FO]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
