CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,F"But I'm not surprised that the jury
OL,8,Fconvicted four of them of criminal
OL,9,Fdamage because they (the jury) weren't
OL,10,Freally given any other options."
OL,12,FThe 22-year-old was cleared of
OL,13,Faggravated burglary and violent
OL,14,Fdisorder in a first trial from
OL,15,FNovember to February, after which she
OL,16,Fwas freed on bail, and cleared of
OL,17,Fcriminal damage following a second
OL,18,Fretrial which concluded in May.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
