OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FIn pre-trial rulings that can now be
OL,8,Freported, Crown Prosecution Service
OL,9,F(CPS) prosecutors said although the
OL,10,Fdefendants didn't face charges under
OL,11,Fanti-terror laws, they believed their
OL,12,Factions had a "terrorism connection".
OL,14,FAt the first court hearing, trial
OL,15,Fjudge Mr Justice Johnson agreed with
OL,16,Fthe CPS assessment, but decided that
OL,17,Fthe terrorism connection would not
OL,18,Fform part of the criminal trial.
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
