OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FSpeaking of her time in custody, Ms
OL,8,FRogers said she was "treated as a
OL,9,Fterrorist" and said she faced book
OL,10,Fbans and was not able to go the gym.
OL,12,F"It (her time in prison) does feel
OL,13,Funjust, but what's happening to my co-
OL,14,Fdefendants is far more unjust," Ms
OL,15,FRogers said.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@JO]tD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
