OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,F"And it's something that everyone
OL,8,Fshould be concerned about because it
OL,9,Fwill set a precedent in UK law where
OL,10,Fyou can be found guilty of something
OL,11,Fas simple as criminal damage and be
OL,12,Fsentenced as a terrorist."
OL,14,FMr Justice Johnson may still be asked
OL,15,Fto consider a terror link to the raid
OL,16,Fwhen he passes sentence on June 12.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@ZO]
