OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FSupporters of the defendants have
OL,8,Fcomplained of a "stitch-up" that
OL,9,Fjurors considering the case during the
OL,10,Ftrial were not told of the terror
OL,11,Fconnection.
OL,13,FA case with a terrorist connection
OL,14,Fwill attract a higher sentence on
OL,15,Fconviction and offenders must notify
OL,16,Fpolice of personal information when
OL,17,Fthey are released, according to the
OL,18,FCPS.
OL,26,@pD@QOUpD@[O]
