OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FMs Rogers said she believes her case
OL,8,Fis being used by the Government to
OL,9,F"justify the proscription of Palestine
OL,10,FAction", which was banned as a
OL,11,Fterrorist organisation in July last
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FThe controversial move was declared
OL,15,Funlawful by the High Court in February
OL,16,Fthis year.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
