OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,FThe Court of Appeal is currently
OL,8,Fconsidering an appeal by the
OL,9,FGovernment, but it is not yet known if
OL,10,Fit will have delivered its ruling when
OL,11,Fthe judge sentences Ms Rogers's co-
OL,12,Faccused next month.
OL,14,F"It's been clear since our arrest that
OL,15,Fthe Government has been using our case
OL,16,Fto justify the proscription Palestine
OL,17,FAction, and since they were humiliated
OL,18,Fin both the press and the public
OL,19,Fcourts, they are trying to justify it
OL,20,Fthrough the back door in our case," Ms
OL,21,FRogers said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,F"I'm concerned not just for my co-
OL,8,Fdefendants, but about the
OL,9,Fdeterioration of the rule of law in
OL,10,Fthis country.
OL,12,F"This is not what happens in a
OL,13,Fdemocracy, and I think everyone should
OL,14,Fbe terrified, quite frankly."
OL,16,FMs Rogers, who had been due to start
OL,17,Funiversity in autumn 2024, said she is
OL,18,Fnot sure what the future holds.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
