CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778731463
OL,3,CI'll never regret what I did `
OL,4,CPalestine Action activist cleared over
OL,5,CElbit raid
OL,7,F"I still have that place at
OL,8,Funiversity, but I don't know, my life
OL,9,Fhas been irrevocably changed by this,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,F"I'm going to continue to support my
OL,13,Fco-defendants who are facing being
OL,14,Fsentenced as terrorists."
OL,16,FShe urged supporters to attend the
OL,17,FJune 12 sentencing for Head, Corner,
OL,18,FKamio and Rajwani, who were remanded
OL,19,Finto custody after being convicted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@fO]tD@AOUvD@YO]
